        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "SQA acceptance criteria — Gradation 2 minimum",
        "description": "Commercial FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical) must hold ISO 9001 or equivalent QMS certification; FDA-developed scripts must be version-controlled under a documented configuration management plan. Gradation 2 requires documented CM and basic regression testing."
      },
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1 is developed under an ISO 9001-certified QMS. FDA in-house pre/post-processing scripts are managed in a git repository with tagged releases and a documented CM plan. Regression tests covering all load-case setups were executed and passed prior to the validation study. Achieved Gradation 3 because independent code review of FDA scripts was also performed."
