        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "NCV acceptance criteria — published benchmark suite",
        "description": "Solver must pass published NAFEMS or equivalent structural benchmark problems for beam bending and contact mechanics at Gradation 2 or above."
      },
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical has been verified against the NAFEMS benchmark suite (LE1, LE10, NL1) for linear and nonlinear structural problems. Contact pair formulation was verified against the Hertzian contact analytical solution. All benchmarks passed within 1% error, meeting Gradation 2 requirements."
    },
    {
