        "description": "Test specimens must be production-representative devices with documented lot traceability. Gradation 2 requires N≥5 per configuration; Gradation 3 requires inter-laboratory replication."
      },
      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were tested across two independent laboratories (FDA OSEL and an ISO 17025-accredited contract lab). Specimens were drawn from a single production lot with full traceability. Inter-laboratory variability was characterized and found to be within ±3% for stiffness, supporting Gradation 3."
    },
    {
