      },
      "rationale": "Stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the exact QoIs specified in the 510(k) submission protocol as design acceptance criteria. The linkage from bench test QoI to clinical performance (resistance to fatigue fracture and permanent deformation) is documented via a failure mode analysis traceable to the device risk management file, achieving Gradation 3."
