        "description": "The validation activities must cover the same device geometry, material, and loading regime as the COU. Gradation 2 requires documented mapping from validation scenario to COU scenario."
      },
      "rationale": "The validation activities directly test the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw under the ASTM F1717 compression-bending protocol, which is identical to the COU. The same FEA model (geometry, material, boundary conditions) is used for both the validation comparisons and the COU predictions. The mapping is one-to-one, meeting Gradation 2."
